# Trivy ignore list — acknowledged vulnerabilities with no available fix
# Review periodically and remove entries once upstream patches are available.
#
# Last reviewed: 2026-04-16

# ncurses buffer overflow — no fix available in Debian 13 (Trixie).
# Affects: libncursesw6, libtinfo6, ncurses-base, ncurses-bin
# Risk: ncurses is not exposed to untrusted input in our BFF container.
CVE-2025-69720

# systemd arbitrary code execution / DoS via spurious IPC — no fix available.
# Affects: libsystemd0, libudev1
# Risk: systemd libraries are present in the base image but the BFF does not
#        run systemd services or use systemd IPC directly.
CVE-2026-29111
